# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build output
# NOTE: dist/ is deliberately NOT ignored. The production VPS deploys by
# pulling this repo and serving dist/ directly, so the built bundle must be
# committed. Run `npm run build` and commit dist/ as part of any release.
